SEARCH
Package it.polimi.ingsw.net

Interface ClientDispatcherInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
ClientDispatcher
public interface ClientDispatcherInterface
The ClientDispatcherInterface interface defines the methods for dispatching server messages to the client. These methods are used to handle different types of messages received from the server.
Author:
Tommaso Trabacchin, Melanie Tonarelli, Emanuele Valsecchi, Adem Shehi
